OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Frather cloudy evening with a few light
OL,7,Fshowers cropping up. Clear spells will
OL,8,Fdevelop overnight, as the showers
OL,9,Flargely die out.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FMost enjoying a dry day with
OL,12,Fgood sunny spells and light winds,
OL,13,Fwith the Central Belt particularly
OL,14,Ffavoured and warm. However, sunshine
OL,15,Fincreasingly turning hazy into the
OL,16,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
