OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMost
OL,6,Fdry during Monday, with hazy sunshine.
OL,7,FHowever, occasional areas of rain
OL,8,Fcrossing the area from the southwest
OL,9,Ffrom late Monday and through Tuesday
OL,10,Fand Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
